  -# Products
  %section.section
    .slide.catalyst
      .container
        %aside{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
          %h2 Products
          %p We are what we create.
          %h5 Crowd Favorites
          %ul.slide-menu
            %li
              = link_to "Catalyst", "#", class: "active"
            %li
              = link_to "Fetch"
            %li
              = link_to "Matchstiq"
            %li
              = link_to "WickedSmart"
        %article
          .content
            %h4 Catalyst
            %p{style: "width: 560px"}
              Catalyst has grown to inspire intrapreneurs and organizations worldwide. Applying HuDiLeDa to business challenges within a workshop setting, Catalyst facilitates fresh thinking and sustainable innovation.
            %header.header-title{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
              2014 Workshops
              %span{style: "width: 528px"}
            %p
              =image_tag "images/catalyst.svg"

    .slide.fetch
      .container
        %aside{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
          %h2 Products
          %p We are what we create.
          %h5 Crowd Favorites
          %ul.slide-menu
            %li
              = link_to "Catalyst"
            %li
              = link_to "Fetch", "#", class: "active"
            %li
              = link_to "Matchstiq"
            %li
              = link_to "WickedSmart"
        %article
          .content
            %h4 Fetch
            %p{style: "width: 560px"} Need to fill jobs fast? Fetch uses SMS technology to reach job-seekers on the go. Set up a campaign online and out go the details with prompts to respond. People can reply that they’re interested, opt out or, if you work at Ignite, try to break the app or mean tweet the Fetch dev team.
            %header.header-title{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
              National Rollout
              %span{style: "width: 558px"}
            %p
              =image_tag "images/fetch.svg"
    .slide.matchstiq
      .container
        %aside{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
          %h2 Products
          %p We are what we create.
          %h5 Crowd Favorites
          %ul.slide-menu
            %li
              = link_to "Catalyst"
            %li
              = link_to "Fetch"
            %li
              = link_to "Matchstiq", "#", class: "active"
            %li
              = link_to "WickedSmart"
        %article
          .content
            %h4 Matchstiq
            %p{style: "width: 560px"} Matchstiq makes hiring a whole lot easier. With job orders, conversations and reports all in one place, hiring managers and recruiters always know where things stand. Tasks like résumé formatting and data crunching are automated, drawing the shortest line possible from “Hey, I need a person” to “You’re hired” and beyond.
            %header.header-title{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
              Team
              %span{style: "width: 488px"}
            %p
              =image_tag "images/matchstiq.svg"
    .slide.wickedsmart
      .container
        %aside{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
          %h2 Products
          %p We are what we create.
          %h5 Crowd Favorites
          %ul.slide-menu
            %li
              = link_to "Catalyst"
            %li
              = link_to "Fetch"
            %li
              = link_to "Matchstiq"
            %li
              = link_to "WickedSmart", "#", class: "active"
        %article
          .content
            %h4 WickedSmart
            %p{style: "width: 560px"} WickedSmart matches students and recent grads to opportunities that build careers, not just résumés.
            %header.header-title{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
              Signups: Students &amp; Alumns Signups:
              %span{style: "width: 738px"}
            %p
              =image_tag "images/wickedsmart.svg"

  %section.section.love
