      %aside{style: "padding-top: 10%"}
        %h2 Jax Love
        %p We helped make these things happen, and we believe in the people behind them.
      %article
        .content
          %h2 Dev + Des
          %h2 AIGA
          %h2 Meros Academy
          %h2 One Spark Innovation
          =image_tag "images/heart.svg"

